    <h2 class="card__title">JWT Fundamentals</h2>
    <p class="card__desc">Deep dive into JSON Web Tokens — structure, algorithms (HS256, RS256, ES256), token entropy, static vs dynamic tokens, and complete authentication workflow.</p>
