      <span class="card__tag card__tag--green">Core Concept</span>
      <span class="card__tag card__tag--blue">Algorithms</span>
      <span class="card__tag card__tag--orange">Entropy</span>
    </div>
  </a>

  <a href="/jwt/owasp-top-10" class="card" id="card-owasp">
    <span class="card__icon">🛡️</span>
    <h2 class="card__title">OWASP Top 10 (2021)</h2>
    <p class="card__desc">Complete breakdown of all 10 vulnerabilities with detailed explanations, real-world examples, exploit POCs, and remediation strategies.</p>
    <div class="card__tags">
      <span class="card__tag card__tag--red">Exploits</span>
      <span class="card__tag card__tag--green">Remediation</span>
      <span class="card__tag card__tag--purple">10 Vulns</span>
    </div>
  </a>

